{"title":"The Rondo Bogan is Designed for All Terrain Touring","link":"https://theradavist.com/rondo-bogan/","date":1717683182000,"content":"<p><img width=\"5582\" height=\"3722\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Rondo_Bogan_ST2.jpg?fit=1200,3722&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Rondo_Bogan_ST2.jpg?w=5582&amp;quality=75 5582w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Rondo_Bogan_ST2.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Rondo_Bogan_ST2.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Rondo_Bogan_ST2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Rondo_Bogan_ST2.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Rondo_Bogan_ST2.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><em>The Rondo Bogan comes in two models, <a href=\"https://shop.rondo.cc/shop/bikes/bogan/prod/rondo-bogan-st-1-22\" target=\"_blank\">ST-1</a> (€2,999 2x drivetrain) and <a href=\"https://shop.rondo.cc/shop/bikes/bogan/prod/rondo-bogan-st-2-22\" target=\"_blank\">ST-2</a> (€2,459 1x drivetrain), fits a 2.1″ 29er tires, and is made from Tange Champion tubing. Like its sibling, the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/the-rondo-ruut-gravel-bike-has-an-adjustable-head-angle/\" target=\"_blank\">Rondo RUUT Gravel</a> it features an adjustable fork offset to tune the off-road ride quality…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"2879\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2635.jpg?fit=1200,1920&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2635.jpg?w=2879&amp;quality=75 2879w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2635.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2635.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2635.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2635.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2635.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img width=\"2879\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2626.jpg?fit=1200,1920&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2626.jpg?w=2879&amp;quality=75 2879w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2626.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2626.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2626.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2626.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/339-2626.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2838\" height=\"914\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Screenshot-2024-06-06-at-8.08.37-AM.png?fit=1200,914&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Screenshot-2024-06-06-at-8.08.37-AM.png?w=2838&amp;quality=75 2838w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Screenshot-2024-06-06-at-8.08.37-AM.png?resize=1200,386&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Screenshot-2024-06-06-at-8.08.37-AM.png?resize=2000,644&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Screenshot-2024-06-06-at-8.08.37-AM.png?resize=768,247&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Screenshot-2024-06-06-at-8.08.37-AM.png?resize=1536,495&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Screenshot-2024-06-06-at-8.08.37-AM.png?resize=2048,660&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>With rack and fender mounts, a portage handle, dropper compatibility, and two fork offset c